{"tid":1009593,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"以學習環境嚟講，邊到學日文最好","createTime":"2019-02-05T09:35:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-05T16:48:13.000Z","uid":53197,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a8d86b8a1c2e1689c14bc0c1d16af65d3371711c","tid":1009593,"uid":53197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T09:35:10.000Z","msg":"我本身自學五十音同基本文法起步都有幾年 但冇好有系統咁學(以前諗住夠睇動漫就得)<br />\n喺u都take過日文course但剩係讀完大家的日本語最淺嗰本<br />\n平時睇動漫/日劇都睇得明一半<br />\n<br />\n而家想的起心肝學得有系統啲 唔想再識啲唔識啲<br />\n我想唔止寫 聽同講都可以handle到<br />\n如果以同學質素 師資 上堂著重方面等等嚟講 有咩學日文嘅地方好推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f959fbd7386be98f821fd52f158ba6ee9cbcd42","tid":1009593,"uid":215634,"like":50,"dislike":1,"score":49,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T09:35:47.000Z","msg":"日本"},{"pid":"40a11e7c2152fccefcecdfa57d9b7e0ed96fb858","tid":1009593,"uid":103049,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T09:54:02.000Z","msg":"柳川日本語學校<br />\n利申係個到讀過，好著重聽講<br />\n時不時有日本人同你上oral堂"},{"pid":"7afe46be64b03f94d4eabaad744b1e1fc501132e","tid":1009593,"uid":129739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f959fbd7386be98f821fd52f158ba6ee9cbcd42","tid":1009593,"uid":215634,"like":50,"dislike":1,"score":49,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T09:35:47.000Z","msg":"日本"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T09:55:19.000Z","msg":"indeed"},{"pid":"dbc38385851e99a0c22dc1b779d2227a83e45a79","tid":1009593,"uid":31575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T10:01:02.000Z","msg":"樓主個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fe196a577c69bb2c2fa855625c4aa7ab02b8ec1","tid":1009593,"uid":133977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7afe46be64b03f94d4eabaad744b1e1fc501132e","tid":1009593,"uid":129739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f959fbd7386be98f821fd52f158ba6ee9cbcd42","tid":1009593,"uid":215634,"like